          <SectionHeadImg>
            <Fragment slot="smltitle">
              Short form video ad design
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="title">
              Crafting compelling video ads.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="desc">
              My Video Ad Production services are all about crafting compelling narratives that captivate your audience's attention. I blend creativity with data-driven insights to create video ads that deliver results. From concept to execution, I've got you covered. In the fast-paced world of digital marketing, video is the name of the game. I'm here to help you harness the power of video ad production to elevate your brand. From conceptualization to shooting and editing, I handle every aspect of your video project with precision. With a deep understanding of what makes a video ad stand out, I'll ensure your content leaves a lasting impact.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="cover">
              <img
                src="/works/video-cameraclose.webp"
                alt="Video ad production on the Gold Coast. Experts in digital marketing campaign production. Complete videography packages for creating ads for Youtube, Facebook and other uses. Video marketing is one of the most effective forms of marketing around right now."
              />
            </Fragment>
          </SectionHeadImg>

          <SectionHeadSecImg>
            <Fragment slot="smltitle">
              Professionally scripted ads
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="title">
              The art of storytelling.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="desc">
              I understand that an effective video ad isn't just about visuals; it's about emotion, connection, and engagement. Whether it's a short, snappy social media ad or a longer-form promotional video, I'll harness the art of storytelling to make your brand message unforgettable. Located on the beautiful Gold Coast, I've had the privilege of working with various businesses seeking professional video ad production services. The golden beaches and lush landscapes provide a stunning backdrop for video shoots, and I know just how to make the most of it. If you're on the Gold Coast and need high-quality video content that speaks to your audience, I'm your go-to expert.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="cover">
              <img
                src="/works/video-filmerdark.webp"
                alt="Improve your Youtube Digital marketing campaigns with video ads produced and filmed on the Gold Coast."
              />
            </Fragment>
          </SectionHeadSecImg>

          <SectionHeadImg>
            <Fragment slot="smltitle">
              Sell your product using video
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="title">
              Video design tailored to your brand.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="desc">
              I work closely with you to understand your goals and vision. From there, I'll develop a video strategy that aligns with your brand identity, delivering video ads that resonate with your target audience and achieve your marketing objectives. Visual appeal is paramount in video ad production. With my background in professional filmmaking, I bring a wealth of technical expertise to the table. From camera angles to lighting and editing, I ensure your videos not only tell a great story but also look visually stunning. This captivating visual experience is what keeps your audience engaged and coming back for more.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="cover">
              <img
                src="/works/video-musicians.webp"
                alt="Web design and video ad production, creating video ads that improve your website conversion rate and work well on Facebook formats. Multiple aspect ratio exports for using your video ad across a wide range of platforms."
